a:11:{i:0;a:3:{s:2:"id";s:3:"who";s:5:"title";s:12:"Who is Jack?";s:10:"paragraphs";a:4:{i:0;a:2:{s:4:"text";s:47:"Jack is a magazine for all ages, men and women.";s:5:"color";s:5:"delta";}i:1;a:2:{s:4:"text";s:562:"Jack is a large poster size format magazine, compose of the carefully selected topics from - fashion / beauty / music / film / art / design / architecture / sports / people - presented in a collectable art form through photography, illustration, typography, graphics and film. The final result is not just one poster but many posters in each issue of the magazine - 30 posters or 60 pages to be exact in the first issue with a centerfold, all quite exciting eye candy material which you will be proud to own, collect, share and display - the best of each season.";s:5:"color";s:10:"quill-gray";}i:2;a:2:{s:4:"text";s:1386:"Jack is a documentary where memoriable moments are captured while making of Jack, edited and will be presented on a network as well as special segments on Youtube, Instagram, Facebook, twitter and other s ocial media. This will be an in-depth study of the making of Jack, formatted in a fast pace exciting story telling manner like the style of go pro with the exception of using better equipment, angle, camera and l ens … show casing production at all levels along with detailed interviews with subject/ artists / stars / personals, focusing on issues that will be relevant to the time frame of that particular issue of Jack. Featured subjects like actors and musicians will tell their stories, collections from fashion designers will be highlighted, models and muse are challenged and worshipped, sportsman revealing their secrets while showing off, make up artists / hair stylist / set designers / wardrobe stylists will discuss about their crafts while educating the world, not forgetting also the crew and team members, editors, invited art directors / creative directors / graphic designers / artists, contributors, location scouts, assistants … all working together towards the creation of magical moments and art while making of Jack magazine. The final product of this documentary will have its own fresh unique language in terms of style, format, editing, music and vibe.";s:5:"color";s:5:"delta";}i:3;a:2:{s:4:"text";s:530:"Jack is a website where all of the above will be collected and documented plus more, elaborating on all topics covered in that particular issue, where the site will bring entertainment, excitement and fresh ideas to anyone visiting, where audience can also participate and share online. The idea is to share with the world what Jack knows best, no one will leave the site unfulfilled. Jack embrace all that is good, from fashion to beauty, film to music, art to design, sports to health, spreading only good to the world + love...";s:5:"color";s:10:"quill-gray";}}}i:1;a:3:{s:2:"id";s:4:"what";s:5:"title";s:13:"What is Jack?";s:10:"paragraphs";a:7:{i:0;a:2:{s:4:"text";s:321:"Jack is a poster size magazine, a collectible piece of art where we collaborate with some of the most talented individuals in the world, where neither politics nor limits exist, where we challenge ourselves and dare to dream. We strive to create with the purest of hearts along with a positive, eager and passionate soul.";s:5:"color";s:5:"delta";}i:1;a:2:{s:4:"text";s:106:"Jack presents the best of each season on Fashion, Beauty, Music, Film, Sports, Design, Art, People + Love.";s:5:"color";s:10:"quill-gray";}i:2;a:2:{s:4:"text";s:75:"There will be 2 issues during the first year, 4 issues each year following.";s:5:"color";s:5:"delta";}i:3;a:2:{s:4:"text";s:262:"Jack first premiere issue (“dare to dream“) will be launched in fall 2014, it consist of 30 posters/60 pages with a cover that consist of a gatefold. Jack’s second issue ( “show n tell”) is also the academy awards issue will be launched in spring 2014.";s:5:"color";s:10:"quill-gray";}i:4;a:2:{s:4:"text";s:155:"Page size is 24” x 18”, Spread size ( poster ) is 24” x 36”, Cover page is 24” x 54” (3 pages), Page count is 60, Center Fold is 36” x 48”.";s:5:"color";s:5:"delta";}i:5;a:2:{s:4:"text";s:34:"All posters printed on both sides.";s:5:"color";s:10:"quill-gray";}i:6;a:2:{s:4:"text";s:397:"Jack magazine maybe packaged in a rolled up format inserted into a tube and packaged within a box with other tubes - think slim cigarettes within the cigarette box, except in this case, a much larger version where the box is covered with collages of images within the magazine, featuring cover story. Jack magazine will also be displayed as a magazines with rod hanging like the ones at a library.";s:5:"color";s:5:"delta";}}}i:2;a:3:{s:2:"id";s:3:"why";s:5:"title";s:9:"Why Jack?";s:10:"paragraphs";a:3:{i:0;a:2:{s:4:"text";s:892:"I do not know, but ever since i was a kid, i have always liked the name Jack, and why not use this name for a magazine? It is easy and simple to remember, spontaneous and definitely friendly where no politics or negativity exist, A magazine where we embrace talented artists and collaborate to create work of arts. For us, Jack magazine has been a l abour of love. It started almost 8 years ago when i felt I needed an outlet for a different kind of expression, something that is apart from my normal creativity where things can get stagnant, predictable and stale … why not create something honest, pure but exciting and fresh, without limits in all genre, using what i already know and mixing taste with history and pop culture influence, along with time and creativity … giving birth to something new exciting and fresh, as so much has been done, recycled and copied. Jack is original.";s:5:"color";s:5:"delta";}i:1;a:2:{s:4:"text";s:642:"I remember while growing up and going to school in England, i came across so many amazing posters on the street and i have tried in vain to tear off quite a few without damaging the posters during the process, unfortunately i was never successful. I wished i could have collected those wonderful posters as they were truly memorable, amazing and cool. I remembered how brilliant their concept were, as well as stung images and cool graphics and art work. I would have collected all and framed them, and would have appreciated them in my study with my school and house mates. I did purchase and collect quite a few posters in my teenage years.";s:5:"color";s:10:"quill-gray";}i:2;a:2:{s:4:"text";s:402:"Here and now, i am making this a reality, where one can easily pick up Jack magazine and enjoy the experience. Fans will now be able to collect Jack, share their experience and participate within jack's network of contributors, readers and fans. Remember, Jack is all about embracing talented people and contributing to promote art, beauty, film, music, sports, entertainment, good life, health + love.";s:5:"color";s:5:"delta";}}}i:3;a:3:{s:2:"id";s:6:"why-me";s:5:"title";s:16:"Why me for Jack?";s:10:"paragraphs";a:6:{i:0;a:2:{s:4:"text";s:488:"My name is xxxxxxx, aka Suzi Simona Menouki, some of you already know who i am, but i want this not to be about me, but about Jack, what is Jack’s integrity and objective, how Jack will showcase it’s ideas about creativity, life and art, how Jack collaborates with some of the most sort after talent in an environment where no limits and boundaries are set, where one’s mind can wonder and expand to the realm of what greatness that artwork maybe - hence, the final product is Jack.";s:5:"color";s:5:"delta";}i:1;a:2:{s:4:"text";s:172:"I would like to facilitate the start up of such a spark, bringing what i know and good into the mix where we will make magic and art - to be presented to the world as Jack.";s:5:"color";s:10:"quill-gray";}i:2;a:2:{s:4:"text";s:808:"I was born in Asia, lived and schooled in England. My passion has always been art, I love to draw and paint, i even worked as an intern to some great artists at Montmartre in Paris … even as a rebellious teen, i love to observe and learn while daring myself how far i would go in my attempt to pursue perfection. i was bold and relentless … and i had so much fun. I speak chinese, studied French language at the Sorbonne university in paris, ventured and taken part in many mischief while residing in London from posh situation to punk environment, and loved every bit of it. I adore the creativity and edge London and Paris has brought to me since my early age and they have somehow settled into my core integrity along with my asian culture and heritage … which all became a very big part of my life.";s:5:"color";s:5:"delta";}i:3;a:2:{s:4:"text";s:401:"While growing up, i embrace the idea of not following the masses but rather, to learn from them and not forget also about our history, to always stay true and strong as an individual. After boarding school, i got accepted to London School of Economics ( LSE ), but I decided it was time for me to see the other side of the world - United States, where i entered UC Berkeley’s school of Architecture.";s:5:"color";s:10:"quill-gray";}i:4;a:2:{s:4:"text";s:1454:"After graduation, i came to New York and embarked on a wild and crazy journey into the world of fashion, beauty, music, film, entertainment and advertising. Through my hard work, discipline and training while being an architectural student, i started experimenting art in many different medium, letter on focusing mainly on visuals, photography and film. I was and i am fortunate enough to have worked with some of the best people in the world, from make up artists, hair stylists, manicurists, set designers, wardrobe stylists, location scouts, producers, assistants … to graphic designers, retouchers, printers, art directors, creative directors, CEOS. I have worked with magazines such as W, Vanity Fair, New York Times, Detail, interview … to L’oreal, Redken, Matrix, Revlon, MAC, Wella, Armani Exchange, Levi’s … I have also worked extensively with personalities like Madonna, Beyonce, Jay Z, Alicia Keys, Mary J, Lenny Kravitz, Jennifer Lopes, Snoop dog, Ludacris, Black Crow, Beck, Julie Delpy, Rosario Dawson, Mark Ronson, kevin Garnett … Every assignment has been a learning experience and my attitude and believe has always been to do my absolute best and give everything i have got into the work. Needless to say, i have always dove into every project like it is the last one, i want to experience and enjoy the process of this creation and collaboration … and nothing has changed here, if anything, only intensified many folds.";s:5:"color";s:5:"delta";}i:5;a:2:{s:4:"text";s:678:"I get so excited and passionate about the possibilities for Jack, what it can and will be, how Jack will change and influence the world. I believe Jack will be an inspiration to anyone who gets a taste of it, where the doors will open and nothing is impossible. I will use my knowledge and experience for Jack in ways i could never have been able to in the past. Jack’s first premier issue is “ dare to dream “ which is what i want for everyone involved in it to explore - without limits, and to have audience relate to it. I hope to mix all culture, beauty, design, philosophy, life, love and peace together, creating a new language that is truly Fresh, one we call Jack.";s:5:"color";s:10:"quill-gray";}}}i:4;a:3:{s:2:"id";s:5:"where";s:5:"title";s:14:"Where is Jack?";s:10:"paragraphs";a:8:{i:0;a:2:{s:4:"text";s:71:"Jack magazine will be available at Jack’s head quarters and showroom.";s:5:"color";s:5:"delta";}i:1;a:2:{s:4:"text";s:49:"Jack magazine can be ordered through the website.";s:5:"color";s:10:"quill-gray";}i:2;a:2:{s:4:"text";s:74:"Jack will be distributed and sold at carefully selected venues and kiosks.";s:5:"color";s:5:"delta";}i:3;a:2:{s:4:"text";s:109:"Jack will be sold and presented in selected boutiques, department stores, hotels, restaurants, coffee houses.";s:5:"color";s:10:"quill-gray";}i:4;a:2:{s:4:"text";s:143:"Jack trunk featuring Jack (magazine, laptop monitors, products) will also be presented like a pop up store in selected existing establishments.";s:5:"color";s:5:"delta";}i:5;a:2:{s:4:"text";s:291:"Jack will make appearance and cover selected Fashion / Film / Music / Art / Sports events and festivals - SBSW, Academy award, Emmys, Grammys, MTV awards, VH1 awars,Canne festival, Sundance film, Tribeca film, Art Basel, Fashion Week ( NYC, London, Paris, Milan, Tokyo, Shanghai ... Global )";s:5:"color";s:10:"quill-gray";}i:6;a:2:{s:4:"text";s:85:"Jack truck will present Jack as a pop up store in selected events, cities, countries.";s:5:"color";s:5:"delta";}i:7;a:2:{s:4:"text";s:127:"Jack is available in United States ( all major cities ), London, Paris, Italy, China, Japan, Middle East, Singapore … global.";s:5:"color";s:10:"quill-gray";}}}i:5;a:3:{s:2:"id";s:3:"how";s:5:"title";s:40:"How will Jack be launched and released ?";s:10:"paragraphs";a:3:{i:0;a:2:{s:4:"text";s:395:"2 weeks prior to the anticipated release of every issue by Jack, there will be allocated wall spaces on the streets to display all of Jack, every single poster from start to finish beginning with the cover, posters and then centerfold. In a location like NYC, Jack will be launched and released near targeted locations like Lincoln center, Soho/Noho, Meatpacking, Union Square, Time Square etc.";s:5:"color";s:10:"quill-gray";}i:1;a:2:{s:4:"text";s:419:"Every Jack issue will be launched with a celebration in a gallery venue where all posters within the new issue will be presented in museum quality archival format and numbered, to be sold to fine arts collectors. Celebration to be followed by an after party event. This will take place in selected cities around the world - NYC, LA, Miami, London, Paris, Milan, Tokyo, Hong Kong, Shanghai, Peking, Singapore … global.";s:5:"color";s:5:"delta";}i:2;a:2:{s:4:"text";s:55:"Special allocated venues from hotel to stores - global.";s:5:"color";s:10:"quill-gray";}}}i:6;a:3:{s:2:"id";s:8:"timeline";s:5:"title";s:16:"Present + Future";s:10:"paragraphs";a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:4:"text";s:121:"Creative Adverti